Note:- JRE contains the JVM (above JVM Components box) plus standard libraries — JRE provides runtime environment.



EXPLANATION :
1. Source Code (.java) → Java programmer code likhta hai.
2. javac Compiler → .java ko .class (Bytecode) me convert karta hai.
3. Bytecode (.class) → Platform-independent code.
4. Class Loader → Bytecode ko JVM me load karta hai.
5. Bytecode Verifier → Check karta hai code safe aur valid hai ya nahi.
6. JIT Compiler → Frequently used bytecode ko machine code me convert karta hai.
7. Native Machine Code → CPU directly execute karta hai.
8. Program Execution → Output milta hai.
